JQ">Phá hoảng - 破幌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%97i/author-5d8o2S_RIMOZD_yipGScpw">Trương Lỗi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-H%E1%BB%AFu-Ph%C3%B9ng/V%C3%A2n-Nam-t%E1%BB%B1-l%E1%BA%A1c-th%C3%A0nh/poem-_HPsLMpsPiF1X00kpybJig">Vân Nam tự lạc thành - 雲南寺落成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-H%E1%BB%AFu-Ph%C3%B9ng/author-bM1XTMtT_e9aq9mDCC9YaA">Trần Hữu Phùng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ph%C3%BA-L%E1%BB%99c-b%C3%A1t-c%E1%BA%A3nh-k%E1%BB%B3-4-Thu%C3%BD-V%C3%A2n-s%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-8qhmweDwZmfxajMMGxuH3w">Vịnh Phú Lộc bát cảnh kỳ 4 - Thuý Vân sơn tự - 詠富祿八景其四－翠雲山寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-quy-s%C6%A1n-k%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%A1nh-H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn/poem-12t-cORGLYn-tdQA6aPMfA">Xuân nhật quy sơn ký Mạnh Hạo Nhiên - 春日歸山寄孟浩然</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br></div>	</div>
